OL,7,FThe 22-year-old, of Edmund Court in
OL,8,FTobermore, denied the charge but was
OL,9,Ffound guilty at Belfast Magistrates'
OL,10,FCourt.
OL,12,FDistrict Judge George Conner said on
OL,13,FWednesday: "I'm well and truly
OL,14,Fsatisfied the words were (not just)
OL,15,Fabusive and insulting, but as a result
OL,16,Fhatred was likely to be stirred up."
