OL,7,FMs McAreavey, the daughter of GAA
OL,8,Ffootball manager Mickey Harte, was
OL,9,Fattacked and killed by an intruder at
OL,10,Fher hotel room while on honeymoon in
OL,11,FMauritius in 2011.
OL,13,FIn May 2022 a number of people were
OL,14,Frecorded taking part in a song about
OL,15,Fher murder.
OL,17,FThe video clip, live streamed from a
OL,18,Fhall in Dundonald, east Belfast during
OL,19,Fevents to celebrate the centenary of
OL,20,Fthe foundation of Northern Ireland,
OL,21,Fprovoked public outrage.
