OL,7,FTwo other men have already pleaded
OL,8,Fguilty and been sentenced for the same
OL,9,Foffence.
OL,11,FSteven Kane, 26, from Coolshinney
OL,12,FHeights in Magherafelt, received a
OL,13,Ffour-month suspended custodial term,
OL,14,Fwhile 23-year-old Cian Jones, of
OL,15,FCraigadick Road in Maghera, was given
OL,16,F240 hours community service.
OL,18,FFootage of the singing, which involved
OL,19,Fmembers of the flute band punching the
OL,20,Fair, was played at previous court
OL,21,Fhearings.
