OL,7,F"He states that because of this
OL,8,Foffending he lost his job which he
OL,9,Ffeels is unfair," she submitted.
OL,11,F"This offence requires a deterrent
OL,12,Fsentence."
OL,14,FKelly's solicitor, Richard Monteith,
OL,15,Fsaid the case had been taken over by a
OL,16,F"media frenzy" and argued that the
OL,17,Findividual who live streamed events
OL,18,Fwas never prosecuted.
