OL,7,FHe accepted the song's lyrics were
OL,8,Foffensive and involved a "warped sense
OL,9,Fof humour".
OL,11,FUrging the judge not to jail his
OL,12,Fclient, Mr Monteith added: "Sending
OL,13,Fhim to prison in the circumstances of
OL,14,Fhow he challenged (the charge) on a
OL,15,Flegal basis is a step too far."
OL,17,FFollowing submissions, Mr Conner
OL,18,Fdecided to impose the maximum 240
OL,19,Fhours community service.
